videos.description: Bruce Brown Jr.  drives and spins to his left for the and-1 basket.
videos.headline: Miami's Brown shows finesse on tough shot

videos.description: Ebuka Izundu speeds down court to clean up the missed shot with a tip-slam.
videos.headline: Miami's Izundu hustles, slams

videos.description: Dewan Huell gets a hand in the passing lane and stuffs it home with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Huell's dunk gives Miami big lead

videos.description: Ebuka Izubdu gives the defender a shoulder fake and banks in the hook shot.
videos.headline: Miami's Izundu fakes defender with nice move for the basket
